data.description: Location, location, location! Come see this remodeled townhome in the heart of Grand Junction. This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is a corner unit and is move-in ready with updates including light fixtures, fans, and laminate flooring. There is even a back patio to enjoy your morning coffee on. Located near  grocery, shopping, restaurants, Colorado Mesa University, and St Mary’s Hospital it doesn’t get much better than this. Comes with 2 reserved parking spaces, a covered carport, and more parking for guests available. HOA Covers water, sewer, trash, pest control, exterior maintenance & common area landscaping and an indoor community pool. Schedule your showing today!
